{"tid":1569883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［會死人架］前線唔好再淨係用6001/3/6罐 滅火隊更加要用7093","createTime":"2019-09-14T19:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T07:19:08.000Z","uid":182994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed154ea28ab5f64c397ae5cd74b35a56ee63eda","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"(新聞) 15歲滅火隊員走入煙霧裏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548958</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成日見到有人好似入面既滅火隊員咁淨係戴「害死人組合」，姐係淨用6001/3/6，<span style=\"color: red;\">係接近冇用架</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLu27Cm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLu27Cm.png&h=5aa11259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（講開6000系，佢地既強度如下：6006&gt;6003&gt;6001，6001絕對唔適合前線使用）<br />\n<br />\n要配個轉接蓋，再加棉<br />\n501蓋就用梯形棉，姐係5N11或者5P71<br />\n502蓋就用P100棉，效果比梯形棉好<br />\n<br />\n詳細型號介紹：<a href=\"https://www.techritual.com/2019/08/10/190809/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techritual.com%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F190809%2F&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=5f4284c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techritual.com/2019/08/10/190809/</a><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: orange;\">滅火隊</span>更加要用防到水既7093棉，唔可以用梯形棉，P100已經係最低消費(但係唔防水，所以濕咗一定要換)<br />\n另外，60926雖然係神裝，但係防水功效其實冇6006罐+7093棉好。<br />\n不過再考慮埋組裝方便程度、輕便性同易賣程度，60926都係滅火之選，不過要有心理準備要換得比較密。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1687zi8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1687zi8.jpg&h=900c57eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b102263c51148f515470265c38401e28b8494a","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e0cc899a017b93b0fbc7ed5731949d2ee057114","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c487ab15412dca340e7c84e8c41df9dd2895202d","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4a6c1f8e944e46c3a0ffff20bf23abb81f096fd","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:52:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"454a90e360d91364a5075beeaa51ad7bc8bad2b2","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"推 今日又有好多"},{"pid":"d694e77973e0a3e6c369ae3453498cecad884567","tid":1569883,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"想問7093棉係指6006入面嘅隔個層棉，定一話出面嘅cover"},{"pid":"04d8b1c607a07dc936829c692f44788fe255c443","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d694e77973e0a3e6c369ae3453498cecad884567","tid":1569883,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"想問7093棉係指6006入面嘅隔個層棉，定一話出面嘅cover"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"加係600x出面架，係兩個灰色既盒<br />\n另外一加多一套502轉接蓋"},{"pid":"a77d3351a827bb1bedb840a0be8e81070e833756","tid":1569883,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d8b1c607a07dc936829c692f44788fe255c443","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d694e77973e0a3e6c369ae3453498cecad884567","tid":1569883,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"想問7093棉係指6006入面嘅隔個層棉，定一話出面嘅cover"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"加係600x出面架，係兩個灰色既盒<br />\n另外一加多一套502轉接蓋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"thx手足，發現對裝好多都唔識，好彩搵到呢篇，但最驚係對眼，近視眼鏡仔冇泳鏡滅多幾粒又要洗一次眼"},{"pid":"6923cef8ecba37e661a35684c51a701fa0d27891","tid":1569883,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77d3351a827bb1bedb840a0be8e81070e833756","tid